'''不列颠哥伦比亚省政府'''是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列颠哥伦比亚省|不列颠哥伦比亚省]]的省级[[政府|政府]]。广义上由省立法机关、省行政机关和省司法机关组成；狭义上特指省行政机关。

== 立法机关 ==

[[不列顛哥倫比亞省議會|不列顛哥倫比亞省議會]]是不列顛哥倫比亞省的立法机关，负责[[加拿大宪法|加拿大宪法]]和其他法律规定的属于本省管辖范围内的立法工作，监督本省行政机关等事务。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.leg.bc.ca/learn-about-us |title=About Us - B.C. Legislative Assembly |accessdate=2020-09-30 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029024043/https://www.leg.bc.ca/learn-about-us |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 行政机关 ==

=== 省行政会议（内阁） ===
省行政会议（内阁）由省长、省行政机关各组成部门主管（各厅厅长）及其他必要人员组成。内阁成员由省长向省督建议，由省督任命；内阁成员通常为省议会议员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/governments/organizational-structure/cabinet/cabinet-ministers |title=Executive Council of the B.C. Government |accessdate=2020-09-30 |archive-date=2020-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209193126/https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/governments/organizational-structure/cabinet/cabinet-ministers |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本届省行政会议现时组成人员共23人。

=== 省行政机关的组成部门 === 
现时省行政机关的组成部门共有20个。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/governments/organizational-structure/ministries-organizations/ministries |title=Ministries of the B.C. Government |accessdate=2020-09-30 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123193747/https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/governments/organizational-structure/ministries-organizations/ministries |dead-url=no }}</ref>

